{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"How to add the package as dependency, import libraries and use theme and components for your apps."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","title":"Getting Started with OUDS","modules":[{"name":"Welcome to Orange Unified Design System"}],"images":[{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"icon"},{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"card"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Integrate-OUDS","text":"Integrate OUDS"},{"type":"heading","text":"Use Swift Package Manager","anchor":"Use-Swift-Package-Manager","level":3},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to add the iOS library of "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Unified Design System","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", you need to add our "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}]},{"text":" into your project.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"To do that, add a new ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"package dependency"}]},{"type":"text","text":" to your "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode"}]},{"type":"text","text":" project by refering to it by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You are free to choose whether or not you want a branch or a specific tag, pick the solution you want."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Orange-OpenSource\/ouds-ios\/wiki\/50-%E2%80%90-About-versions,-releases-and-builds"},{"type":"text","text":" for more details about versions, releases and tags. You can find release tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0"}]},{"type":"text","text":") and release candidates tags (e.g. "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.0.0-rc3","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Import-the-librairies-you-need","level":3,"text":"Import the librairies you need"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You should use one (or several) of the following imports for your needs, which are basically "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" products."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"tip","name":"Tip","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"We recommend to embed in your apps only the ones you need to avoid to embed useless assets.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["import OUDSThemesContract \/\/ If you want to define your theme, use themes or OUDSThemeableView","import OUDSModules \/\/ To use modules","import OUDSComponents \/\/ To use components","import OUDSThemesOrange \/\/ To use the default Orange theme","import OUDSThemesOrangeCompact \/\/ To use the Orange Compact theme","import OUDSThemesSosh \/\/ To use the Sosh theme","import OUDSThemesWireframe \/\/ To use the Wireframe theme","import OUDSTokensComponent \/\/ If you need to override or use directly components tokens","import OUDSTokenSemantic \/\/ If you need to override or use directly semantic tokens","import OUDSTokensRaw \/\/ If you need to override or use directly raw tokens","import OUDSFoundations \/\/ For some utilities"]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Or more simple, import umbrella library","anchor":"Or-more-simple-import-umbrella-library"},{"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"We do not recommend this solution because from our point of view use of tailored imports is better to import only the needed elements."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"use of umbrella products can increase app sizes and needed storage because it emebds plenty of assets (images, fonts, etc.)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and useless constants."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Import the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift Package"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" product which suits your needs:"}]},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Umbrella"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUI"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above and all themes"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Orange Compact themes"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIWireframe"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All librairies listed above but with only Wireframe theme","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDSSwiftUIOrangeSosh"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"All librairies listed above but with only Orange and Sosh themes"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Chose-your-theme","text":"Chose your theme"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange Unified Design System"}]},{"type":"text","text":" framework provides today four themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Theme"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Description"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Orange"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The default one for Orange products and can be enriched \/ derivated"}]}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For some Orange products with heavy \/ rich UI and dimensions constraints"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sosh"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For Sosh products"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Wireframe"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For mockups, prototypes and prooves of concepts witouth Orange-flavoured styles","type":"text"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Apply-a-theme","level":3,"text":"Apply a theme"},{"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You will need to use for your application root view the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/oudsthemeableview\/"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/ouds\/themes"},{"type":"text","text":" also."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This special view is here to define some elements as environment variables and injects the choosen theme."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"syntax":"swift","code":["@main","struct YourApp: App {","    var body: some Scene {","       WindowGroup {","          OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","          }","       }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}]}]},{"type":"row","numberOfColumns":2,"columns":[{"size":1,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then get the current applied theme in your views and use the tokens you want."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The tokens are wrapped in providers with clear names, you only need to choose the ones you want."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"size":1,"content":[{"syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Use it in views as an environment variable","@Environment(\\.theme) var theme"],"type":"codeListing"}]}]},{"style":"tip","name":"Tip","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Keep in mind only one theme can be used within one ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSThemeableView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Trick-for-Xcode-Preview","level":3,"text":"Trick for Xcode Preview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you use Xcode ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"text":" blocks, you will have to be sure the theme is instanciated and injected through the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because it is not possible today to override the legit ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"#Preview"},{"text":" block, you can instead use some of our utilities to wrap your content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"inside the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSThemeableView"},{"text":" automatically. These utilities come with the themes modules. Without them you may face errors about undefined theme.","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Apply Orange theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangePreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Orange Compact theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .orangeCompactPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Sosh theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .soshPreview()","}","","\/\/ Apply Wireframe theme","#Preview {","    SampleView()","        .wireframePreview()","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Themes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Components","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Modules"],"anchor":"Essentials","generated":true}],"references":{"ic_component_intro.png":{"identifier":"ic_component_intro.png","type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_component_intro.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"ic_theme_intro.png":{"identifier":"ic_theme_intro.png","type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_theme_intro.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/Tokens":{"role":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/tokens","title":"Tokens","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_design_token_intro.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"ic_design_token_intro.png"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Design tokens represent the small, repeated design decisions that make up a design system’s visual style. Tokens wrap hard-coded static values, such as hexadecimal codes for color, with self-explanatory names. They are used to define the look and feel and the style of everything. They are exposed through the themes and can be used as they are."}],"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/Tokens"},"ic_unified_ds.png":{"identifier":"ic_unified_ds.png","type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_uni